Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:01.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.93,0:00:03.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:06.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,People are trying to eat lunch,\Nso please stop...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.56,0:00:10.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing is believing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:11.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:13.24,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear witness!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:16.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Big relief, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:19.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka being back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:20.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:22.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:24.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's all the fuss about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:27.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, Valentine's Day is coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:30.21,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,These giddy youngsters\Nwon't hear a word I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:31.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:33.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- You can't fool me!\N- Teach...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:39.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll start fawning over each other\Nthe second my back is turned!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:42.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Public displays of affection at school...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:48.31,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, there's no point in giving or\Ngetting chocolates at school...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:51.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,School is for learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:53.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're being lectured by Haruta?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:56.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I say something wrong again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:58.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What's school for, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:01:00.08,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Health and gym?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:02.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:04.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, Aisaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:06.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come to the reception\Noffice after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:12.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,(My Silky Love)\NEvery time I think of you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:12.05,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,MY SILKY LOVE nijuu yojikan zutto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:15.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,(My Silky Love)\Nfor 24 hours straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:15.55,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,MY SILKY LOVE kimino koto omoutabi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:19.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,(My Silky Love)\NIt only makes me feel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:19.09,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,MY SILKY LOVE modokashii kono kimochi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.09,0:01:23.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,(My Silky Love)\Nthat much more impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.09,0:01:23.06,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,MY SILKY LOVE tada afure kaetteku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:29.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so simple just to say I love you.\NBut when you come close to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:29.94,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,sukito ieba kantan nanoni\Nkimiga maeni kichauto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:36.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,my own emotions go awry\Nand get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:36.99,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kyaraga sobie watashino\Nkoto wo jamashiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:44.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I can bring myself to do anything.\NThat's who I'm supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:44.62,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,itsumonaraba tsuyoki de ikeru\Nsonna seikakunanoni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:50.88,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But I just can't break this\Nwall down no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:50.88,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,donna ganbatte mitemo kabewa kuzusenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:54.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Please understand these feelings for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:54.46,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,sasshite hoshii kono kimoch iwo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:57.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why these gazes of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:57.93,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,dakara watashi wa itsumo kimini
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:01.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,they tell my love for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:01.68,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,daisuki dayoto okuru shisen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:05.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Now gather up my courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:05.60,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,saidaino yuukide
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:09.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A fragile heart made of silk,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:09.14,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,yabure souna shirukuno haato
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.14,0:02:12.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that by meeting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.14,0:02:12.69,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kimini atte kizuita yatto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:18.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so clumsy when it comes to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:18.40,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,ainiwa bukiyou dattan datte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:23.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A forgotten scar left in my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:23.16,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,wasure kaketa koino kizuato
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:26.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,and I suddenly felt it sting deep inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:26.70,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kyuuni uzuki dashitano kyunto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:31.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say that I love you someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:31.17,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,itsukawa watashi rashiku sukito iwanakya
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:36.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Or it'll keep making me weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:36.01,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,imayori yowaku nacchauyo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:42.18,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Path to Take
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:42.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, you still haven't\Nfinalized your career plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:46.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And Aisaka-san, you never turned one\Nin at the beginning of the school year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:49.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm still talking it over with my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:53.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,How does she feel? She wants\Nyou to go to college, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:54.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:59.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother has been pushing herself\Ntoo hard for too many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:02.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want her to suffer anymore,\Nso I'm not going to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:08.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And why haven't you turned\Nin yours, Aisaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:14.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rich, so I'll never need to work.\NMeaning there's no need to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:16.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I even want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are the two of you so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:20.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Not going to college isn't that—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:21.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:27.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just, what you do with your lives\Nis completely up to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.90,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No more blaming others for what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:30.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The responsibility is all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:33.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want you to give\Nthis careful consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:38.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never gone against your\Nmother's wishes before, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.82,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring your career plans to the\Nfaculty office when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.82,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Reception Office
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:47.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of my life, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you—?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:52.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:54.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the form we're supposed to turn in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:55.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:06.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need that crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:10.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can think about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:13.81,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I have enough problems as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:20.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always, always denied who I am,\Nand wondered why I turned out this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:22.42,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What could I have done differently?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:31.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even figure out what\NI want to do {\i1}right now{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:35.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,There is one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:38.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to experience a normal love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But don't you have someone...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:45.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:46.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:48.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't think of anybody off the top of my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:51.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be born into a normal household,\Nand grow up to be a normal girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:54.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Then meet and get to know\Na guy in a normal fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:58.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of love\NI wanted to experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why past tense?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said. It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:03.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was wrong from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:05.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:07.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:10.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there even a right way?\NA wrong way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:11.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Who decides that anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:15.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you suddenly lecturing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:20.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't my intention...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:24.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your career plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:26.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn about that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:36.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:41.11,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I already said I won't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:45.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Kawashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:46.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you reconsider?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to deal with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:51.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me, sir, I must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:53.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kawashima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:55.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you just standing there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Go after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:58.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:12.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do with my shoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:14.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a shoe fetish?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:16.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:19.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:26.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you trying to set a record\Nin shoe throwing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:28.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I already apologized.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:31.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:34.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you called to the faculty office?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:40.08,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I refused a request to model our school\Nuniform for next year's brochure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that your thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:44.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:48.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, who knows how long\NI'll be at this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:52.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're still hung\Nup on your fight with Kushi—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:56.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A peon like Kushieda Minori\Ncould never affect my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:12.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd originally planned to leave\Nthis school after the first term.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:15.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the mess with the\Nstalker had died down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:17.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You never mentioned anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:20.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided I'd like to stay a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:25.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could, I'd stay here\Nwith everyone forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:27.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:33.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Taiga getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:39.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was the only one who understood her,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.03,0:07:41.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,then I had to be the one to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Or so I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:44.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:49.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I now see that everything would've\Nworked out just fine without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:52.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:59.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the bar be fine without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And my shift at the bakery...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:13.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,They even had a cute uniform for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:17.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I called both. Don't worry about a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:19.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:23.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-How i-is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:26.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya-chan's sleeping, so shush.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.11,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:30.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji, how is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:32.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:37.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It scared me so much when I looked through\Nthe window and saw her collapse...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:38.95,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:41.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:43.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,To buy something for Yasuko to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:47.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:49.71,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:06.90,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't bring your wallet, keys, phone,\Nor even your dumb grocery bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:10.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it together, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:13.11,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and put this on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:16.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:21.54,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You should take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:22.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine! You wear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:27.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:28.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:29.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:31.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:33.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home. I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:34.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:35.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:36.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go home, okay!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:45.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:46.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:50.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko collapsed because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:52.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm to blame...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:53.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:55.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She's anemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:57.45,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:59.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's not your fault!\N- If I were more responsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:03.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If Yasuko were willing to trust me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:08.54,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If she would just rely on me...\NThis never would've happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:11.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:19.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:28.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What...am I supposed to—?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:29.81,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be...okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:38.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it will!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:41.95,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:45.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I'm a super mommy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:57.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:03.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:06.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,There's somewhere I need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:12.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be swamped the next couple days on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,account of it being Valentine's and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:16.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry. She won't be able to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:20.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Doubt I'll be able to find someone\Nto cover her shift...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:21.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:26.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:28.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:30.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Man, you're a lifesaver!\N- Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not doing this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:36.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help Ya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me work too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:42.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:47.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I was fired from my job at the bakery?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:48.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:51.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well. These things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:53.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find another job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:55.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why am I the one being consoled?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:04.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wel-c-co—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:06.24,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's selling...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to be louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:15.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to compensate for a face that\Nwas never meant for customer service.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:19.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, you're actually working!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:21.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Taka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:22.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you—?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruta-kun, which one do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:28.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that if you get greedy and buy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a big one, something bad will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:32.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, I'll take the big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:35.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,May I please have this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:38.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That'll be 580 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:40.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You have an older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:42.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:43.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:44.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, have fun working.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:49.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is cold outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go someplace warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.45,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Good plan.\N- Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:54.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,There is seriously something\Nwrong with this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:56.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Noto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:57.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:00.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No reason. Just happened\Nto be in the area...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:02.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:04.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen anyone else around?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:06.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Ami-chan, or the lovely Nanako...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:09.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't seen Kihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:09.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:11.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I just, y'know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:16.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wondered if she's going nuts about\Ngiving Kitamura chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:18.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I personally care!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:22.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't! But Tiger, you're worried, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:23.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,About, y'know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:25.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I be worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:29.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And why do you care if Kihara Maya\Ngives Kitamura-kun chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:30.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:33.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in love with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:38.08,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So after all those fights, you suddenly\Nfound yourself attracted to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:40.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, didn't think that actually happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just wrong, Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:45.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing wrong about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfectly natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:49.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,When a male stamen and a female pistil—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:50.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:55.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:58.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:00.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We better sell some stuff\Nbefore we get yelled at.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:02.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:05.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to summon the lethal weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:06.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:09.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:10.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:11.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.24,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:15.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll even let you hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:17.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Screw that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:18.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me do weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:21.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gorgeous, so I'm bound\Nto attract attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. You're positively stunning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:24.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The center of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:30.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And say, "I love the chocolate here!"\Nas loud as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:32.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to advertise?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:33.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:34.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:36.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I do something so stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Be nice, Dumb-chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:39.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Or, I know. Buy another one\Nwith your own money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:42.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And give it to Minorin to make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:46.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been watching you a lot\Nmore closely than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:49.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're having a difficult time\Nmaking up with Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:51.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Chihuahua heart quivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:52.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:53.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make stuff up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:56.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If it makes you uncomfortable,\NI'll call Minorin for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:59.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, Valentine's Day came\Nat such a perfect time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:00.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:02.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is that Kawashima Ami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:03.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:06.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She's adorable! Look at that cute face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she buying chocolates from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:11.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I love these chocolates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:14.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,My model friends all rave about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:15.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna buy some!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The same kind as Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:19.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, she knows what she's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:20.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:21.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:24.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll be right with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:26.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji, what are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I'd like this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:29.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:31.95,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kawashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:35.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like to chase people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:38.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You have stalker potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:41.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And you really like to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:44.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're running from a lot more than just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:47.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to be clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:52.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never wanted you gone or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:52.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:56.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will be disappointed if you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:58.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:01.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,"Everyone"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:03.90,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:09.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:13.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Taiga's getting overwhelmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:15.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:23.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't want {\i0}everyone{\i1} to like me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:27.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess...I don't get it, either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:30.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:31.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,See you two tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:34.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We reached our quota, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:37.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to buy the rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:38.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna pass them out as gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:40.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Gifts?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I ruined the trip for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:48.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun, Minorin,\Nand Dumb-chi, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:50.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:55.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to give you chocolates,\Nwould you be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:57.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:00.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:05.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have to be a heartless bastard to not be\Nhappy about you giving me chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:07.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:08.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:13.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hand them out as-is.\NMaybe I'll try to make them special.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:18.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope everyone likes them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:22.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Something smells good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going back to work already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:27.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry. I'm in tip-top shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:30.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to thank Taiga-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:45.21,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:49.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning,\Ngathering us all here like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:56.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Valentine's Day today, so I made\Nchocolates to show my appreciation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:58.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Made? By yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:01.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it'd be a shame to eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:04.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't those the chocolates\Nyou were selling yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.31,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've finally learned to lie—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:07.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:11.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I reused the boxes because they're pretty,\Nbut I made the chocolates myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:13.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Dumb-chi, this one's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your help yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:16.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll never happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday was a special case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:19.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:24.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you came to save\Nme during the class trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:25.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, what's with all the formality?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:31.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:32.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:34.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:36.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Same deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:37.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:40.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Share with Ya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:43.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And Kitamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:48.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving you the one that turned out best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:49.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:54.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who carried me up the cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:19:00.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crap, I didn't tell Kushieda...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:02.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Were my eyes rolled back in my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:07.71,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I had absolutely no idea what\Nwas going to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:10.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept rolling and rolling until I hit my\Nhead and there was this whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:13.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be how it feels to get knocked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:15.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's feels almost like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:19.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,For a while, I thought I'd blurted\Nout all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:22.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally panicked when I came to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:24.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly do you think you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:28.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I could never tell you! Never, ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:29.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:30.89,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, spill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:33.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! I mean, it was just my imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:34.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:37.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I can never let anyone find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:39.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If they ever knew, I'd be ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:42.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So completely I could no longer live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:43.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:45.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You didn't hear me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, I didn't hear a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:48.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:50.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody heard a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:59.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:01.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to pretend you didn't hear her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:03.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying, Minorin?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:06.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:08.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to blindly accept this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:10.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun was the one who saved you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:11.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But he didn't tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:14.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of whatever it is that you're hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Taiga!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:19.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why can't you just be honest and admit it!?\N- Let...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:20.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,...me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:28.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:34.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Man, that's one sorry face.\N- Dumb-chi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:34.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.34,0:20:39.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you fine with letting\NAisaka go right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:40.71,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:43.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:45.43,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- No!\N- What do you see!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:49.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- No! No! No! No! No!\N- I'm Minori! Your best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:51.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you love me, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:54.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Let me go! Let me go!\N- Then trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:57.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Let me go!\N- I trust you, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:20:59.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep going on and on about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:03.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not so weak you'd blame\Nothers for giving up on what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:05.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Or am I wrong!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:07.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:10.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:13.08,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I want my best friend to be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:14.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:20.71,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The responsibility for my happiness\Nlies with me and me only!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:24.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone else decide\Nwhat makes me happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:31.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We've done all we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:33.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:37.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:39.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Amin, you sellout!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:40.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Better chase her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:42.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're up to the task.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:46.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, I'm going after Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:49.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done talking to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:50.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:55.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What...What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.21,0:21:58.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Find out how Taiga feels...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:21:59.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, then what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:04.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Taiga wanted to hide her feelings...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:06.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:09.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:12.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,In those sleepless nights,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:12.93,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,nemurenai yoruni wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:16.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I lay there sighing all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:16.19,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,hitoride tameiki
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:19.81,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What about everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:19.81,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,minna wa dounano
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:23.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It just feels so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:23.61,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,nandaka samishii
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.61,0:22:30.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A tiny little seed in this huge Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.61,0:22:30.07,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,hiroi daichini hitotsubu no tane
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:33.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Stretch out those roots,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:33.33,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,nekko nobashite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:40.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,and bear a fruit that's still unripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:40.96,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,mada aoi miwo tsuketa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:45.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The fruit that wants to hurry and turn orange.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:45.84,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,orenji ironi hayaku naritai kajitsu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.84,0:22:49.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Showering in your light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.84,0:22:49.13,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kimino hikari wo abite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.13,0:22:52.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,only nurtures bigger ideals and dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.13,0:22:52.68,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,risou ya yume wa fukuramu bakari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:56.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:56.06,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kizuiteyo nee
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:02.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate the orange today but cried\Nbecause it was still too sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:02.94,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,orenji kyoumo tabete mitakedo\Nmada suppakute naita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.02,0:23:06.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It reminded too much of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.02,0:23:06.40,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,watashi mitaide nokosenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:08.82,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,so I finished the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:08.82,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,zenbu tabeta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:15.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you. It makes me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:15.41,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,sukidayo nakeruyo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:22.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:22.25,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,sukidayo sukidayo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:26.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.80,0:23:28.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:30.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I left the laundry hanging outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:32.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:35.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I've left a lot of things hanging.
